summary.label:
Click around the screen to make the alpaca jump left or right.The higher the score, the faster the steps fall. How many levels can you pass?
You can get a new image of alpaca by going through the customs, and the alpaca will be more lovely in the future;
Attention, identify the direction of the steps, do not fall, be careful of obstacles and props!

Props and obstacles:
（1）Roadblock: If you run down, you will fail. Please detour;
（2）Floor nail:Wait it will disappear after 3 seconds;
（3）Exchange direction：Switch left and right directions,be careful;
（4）Cheese：eat cheese to gain more score;

The physical picture level and more interference factors not only make the game more challenging, but also make the game closer to reality. Use your detective cells to find the difference and challenge one by one.

- Effectively exercise your eyesight and brain;
- Beautiful illustration style, easy and casual decompression;
- Challenge with family and friends, not only fun but also emotional.

Everyone is looking for Find Diff 2, welcome to challenge!
